			>
			<DIV>OH, one more.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Summon Rod of domination</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Class: Enchanter, Magician, Necromancer</DIV>
<DIV>Required level: 63</DIV>
<DIV>Equipable: Primary</DIV>
<DIV>Stats: dmg 10, delay 20, 100 hps/100 mana</DIV>
<DIV>No Rent</DIV>
<DIV>Effect:&nbsp; Increases duration of the charm line of spells by 30%</DIV>
<DIV>Focus Effect: Obscurity of Marr:&nbsp; Decreases hate by 600</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Usable only when grouped with a Magician.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Thanks,</DIV>
<DIV>Ninka</DIV>	
